author: Dan Molinski
title: U.S. Crude Stocks Unexpectedly Fall, Gasoline Rises
text:
U.S. crude stockpiles unexpectedly declined in the week ended Aug. 21, according to data released Wednesday by the U.S. Energy Information Administration.
